Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既沒有想成為愛麗絲的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有要戰鬥的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然沒有身為薔薇少女的使命和驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就消失吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看一看吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們並不想要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為姐妹  同樣是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們並不想相互憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想相互傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…因為我們是…薔薇少女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是負責供給力量的存在而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  力量還在繼續湧出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  我還…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會…在沒有注意到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經使用了小惠的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石所承受的痛苦  可並非僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…要做到這種地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅在哪裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:04:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼奪走了蒼星石的薔薇聖母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼和薔薇水晶聯手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？那不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是薔薇少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了成為愛麗絲  去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗者會變成廢物！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你應該知道被傷害的痛楚和戰鬥的痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯！我知道的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我被你傷害過！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我停止戰鬥與你和好？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個沒用的媒介家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起共享天倫之樂？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要開玩笑了  你認為我會做這種事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的憎恨  不是一兩句話就可以消除的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我記住  我是水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你變成廢物的  將會是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…要打倒…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…父親大人說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有…成為愛麗絲的資格…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是這幅身體…也可以成為愛麗絲的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…小惠…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被翠星石吸引過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈的媒介？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有薔薇聖母…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有薔薇聖母…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她才…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  就只剩下你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都…是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒有做這種事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有  做這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經足夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是姐妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都同樣是人偶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲有多好  這我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那對於你們來說是多麼重要的東西  我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果說你們是只為了戰鬥而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是錯誤的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…讓大家…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊！如果你也這麼做的話不就和她一樣了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不希望你們繼續戰鬥下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅的…薔薇聖母…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你勝利了  薔薇水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人偶勝利了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能變成比薔薇少女更好的人偶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:12:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個羅真
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於做出了更加強大  更加美麗的人偶！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然  這手臂我會給你修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比…羅真還…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是羅真嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅真？我是比羅真更高位的存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最強的人偶師！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越了一直無人能超過的吾師！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾…師…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅真的徒弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}痛不痛…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…真紅她們是被欺騙了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為了這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好！把真紅她們修好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這種無聊的事…我是不會允許的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:14:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！只不過是個偶然成為真紅媒介的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼狂妄自大！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒辦法理解吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種什麼都無法創造出的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在那裡安靜的看著吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看最強的人偶誕生的瞬間！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇水晶  你是我的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我製作出的  最好的傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼美麗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口…好…好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉…裂開了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇水晶  把薔薇聖母拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會壞掉的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣！我最重要的人偶！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於虛偽而言  真實的光輝好像過於耀眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉普拉斯之魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你全都知道嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的遊戲時間  這次也就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說有趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能繼續漂泊了吧  直到找到新的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡毀滅之前  回到現實世界去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅上過發條的庶人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能阻止你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓你繼續戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！羅真！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那隻兔子一起在看著吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你想要的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是為了這樣  才製作人偶的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我！羅真！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都深愛著你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從幾十年  幾百年之前開始就一直愛著你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只追尋著你  只夢到你的身影啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快回答我些什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她們必須愛著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  我見到父親大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人對我說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「再次為了愛麗絲而努力吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  並非必須經過愛麗絲遊戲  才能成為愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也會變回原來的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  被薔薇水晶擊敗的都會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石和雛莓…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我從現在開始必須背負的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人是為此把我修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說要讓我解決這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名偵探庫庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}庫庫偵探～人偶們的鎮魂歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  庫庫偵探要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
